## Server and Network Components (Proprietary)

The game server, matchmaking services, and certain network synchronization
libraries are proprietary and not included in this repository. These components
are required for online multiplayer but not for local play.

The open-source client includes:
- Full single-player functionality
- Local multiplayer (same machine)
- LAN play capabilities
- All gameplay mechanics and physics

## Third-Party Assets

Third-party assets (3D models, textures, fonts, etc.) are used under their
respective licenses. See individual asset directories for license details.

Most assets are CC0/Public Domain or similarly permissively licensed.

